headline: Asian Stocks Bounce Back After Worst Day on Record: Markets Wrap
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Asian shares bounced back after the worst day on record, as Japan lead gains on expectations that it will get priority in trade talks with US President Donald Trump’s administration.
